snippet.title: Final Fantasy VI/6/3 commercial (japanese)
snippet.description: This is a japanese commercial for another great game called Final Fantasy VI/6/3 Just had to add that number thing :D It's the SNES or Super famicon version. The music is "Roaming Sheep" from "FFIII: Yuukyuu no Kaze Densetsu" OST thanks for supermogl. You can listen to the full version here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0qtJqI_IjPA&feature=related
